OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,FA junior analyst at Southampton has
OL,7,Fclaimed he "didn't really have an
OL,8,Foption" but to spy on the club's
OL,9,FChampionship rivals in a move which
OL,10,Fsparked the 'Spygate' scandal.
OL,12,FSaints were last month thrown out of
OL,13,Fthe play-off final for spying on semi-
OL,14,Ffinal opponents Middlesbrough. A
OL,15,Fsubsequent appeal was rejected, with
OL,16,Fthe League Arbitration Panel's written
OL,17,Freasons published on Monday.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@GO]
