FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,FThe south-coast club then questioned
OL,7,Fthe independence of the panel, which
OL,8,Fincluded David Winnie, who played one
OL,9,Fgame for Boro in 1994. He said, in a
OL,10,Fstatement to the Press Association
OL,11,Flast month, that suggestions he could
OL,12,Fbe influenced were "wholly without
OL,13,Ffoundation".
OL,15,FThe 39-page written reasons set out
OL,16,Fwhy Southampton spied on Oxford,
OL,17,FIpswich and Middlesbrough, along with
OL,18,Fwhat type of information was
OL,19,Fdiscovered.
OL,26,@tD@TOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,FIt also laid bare the influence of
OL,7,FSaints head coach Tonda Eckert and
OL,8,Fsaid it had been "a contrived and
OL,9,Fdetermined plan from top down to gain
OL,10,Fa competitive advantage".
OL,12,FIt continued: "These junior members of
OL,13,Fstaff felt compelled to do what they
OL,14,Fwere very uncomfortable doing because
OL,15,Fthey considered their jobs would
OL,16,Fotherwise be at risk."
OL,18,FThe written reasons stated junior
OL,19,Fstaff felt "pressurised to do the
OL,20,Fobservations that Mr Eckert and the
OL,21,Fsenior coaches wished them to do".
OL,26,@pD@ROUrD@XO]tD@OOUxD@VO]{D@LOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
