PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,FIn one WhatsApp exchange, an analyst
OL,7,Fmessaged an intern: "Try and make out
OL,8,Fas much as you can please. You legend.
OL,9,FManager loved it."
OL,11,FIt was alleged that Eckert wanted to
OL,12,Fknow whether Oxford caretaker Craig
OL,13,FShort would play with a back four or
OL,14,Fback five before their Boxing Day
OL,15,Fclash and if Cameron Brannagan was fit
OL,16,Ffor the U's, which resulted in a
OL,17,Fjunior analyst intern being asked to
OL,18,Fwatch Saints' opponents train.
OL,26,@oD@UOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
