OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,F"In his evidence to the Commission,
OL,7,Fthe junior analyst intern said: "I
OL,8,Fdidn't really have an option and
OL,9,Fwasn't provided an opportunity to say
OL,10,Fno... I was an intern and was doing
OL,11,Fwhat I was told."
OL,13,FIt was also revealed that an analyst
OL,14,Fat Southampton was provided with
OL,15,FEastleigh kit in order to watch
OL,16,FIpswich train at Eastleigh's ground
OL,17,Fbefore a 2-2 draw on April 28 at St
OL,18,FMary's. Footage of the training
OL,19,Fsession was also provided to Saints
OL,20,Fand allowed them to predict the
OL,21,FIpswich starting line-up.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
