FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,FEckert was also accused of wanting to
OL,7,Fwatch Middlesbrough's training session
OL,8,Fto determine if Hayden Hackney was
OL,9,Finvolved.
OL,11,FThe written reasons stated the junior
OL,12,Fanalyst intern, who was again chosen,
OL,13,F"felt under extreme pressure due to
OL,14,Fthe context of the importance of the
OL,15,Fgame for the club".
OL,17,FIt added: "He feared that he might be
OL,18,Fdismissed by the club or it might
OL,19,Fotherwise adversely affect his career
OL,20,Fif he did not do it. So, he went."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@RO]yD@KOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
