PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,FA statement by Southampton
OL,7,Facknowledged they "breached the
OL,8,Frelevant regulations" but questioned
OL,9,Fthe composition of the League
OL,10,FArbitration Panel, which included
OL,11,FWinnie.
OL,13,F"What is harder to accept is that
OL,14,Fsimilar scrutiny does not appear to
OL,15,Fhave been applied to the composition
OL,16,Fof the disciplinary panel itself,
OL,17,Fgiven the apparent historic and
OL,18,Findirect connections of two panel
OL,19,Fmembers to Middlesbrough," the Saints
OL,20,Fstatement read.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@UO]uD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
