PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780427467
OL,3,CSouthampton junior analyst 'felt under
OL,4,Cextreme pressure' to spy
OL,6,F"While those connections do not by
OL,7,Fthemselves prove bias, they plainly
OL,8,Fraise legitimate questions about
OL,9,Fconsistency, perception and the
OL,10,Fstandards of independence expected in
OL,11,Fproceedings of this magnitude."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
